            "heading": "Stock Premium AirVape Vaporizers at Competitive Wholesale Pricing",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_WdDyKH": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Partner with AirVape to access premium vaporizers and accessories through a wholesale program designed for retailers, resellers, distributors, and serious trade partners.</p><p>We offer flexible wholesale solutions based on product type, order quantity, and business requirements, helping partners source premium products with competitive pricing and scalable opportunities.</p><p>Whether you are looking for standard products or exploring larger-volume orders, AirVape is built to support long-term wholesale growth.</p>"
          }
