          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Documents Required for Wholesale Setup",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "heading_html_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "text_KNcmRd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To review and process wholesale inquiries, businesses may be asked to provide basic company and trade information, including:</p><ul><li>Business name and contact details</li><li>Company registration or trade license</li><li>Tax or VAT certificate, where applicable</li><li>Shipping and billing address</li><li>Sales channel details, such as website, marketplace, or store information</li><li>Product interest and estimated order quantity</li></ul><p>Providing complete and accurate information helps us review your request more efficiently.</p>"
          }
        }
