            "answer": "<p>Yes. The MOQ can vary by product. Standard products may have a lower MOQ, while customized or branded orders may require a higher minimum quantity. Our wholesale MOQ depends on the product type, packaging requirements, and shipping destination. Please contact us with your product details so we can confirm the exact MOQ.</p>"
